{
  "id": "adv_card_cca_01_01",
  "title": "ココア",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bell-03.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございました！\n……ふぅ、お客さん、落ち着いたね",
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "みんながお使いに行ったタイミングで\n沢山お客さんが来てビックリしたね",
      "startTime": 9.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.3490093867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんとすみれちゃんがいてくれたから\nなんとかなったよ～！　ありがとう！",
      "startTime": 15.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.4825096448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、私の方こそありがとう。ココアちゃんと\nチノちゃんが丁寧に教えてくれたおかげだよ",
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 26.7322372437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうかなぁ。お姉ちゃんだと思って\nもっともっと頼ってくれていいからね？",
      "startTime": 30.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.8189036687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ありがとう\nでも、お姉ちゃんはもういるから大丈夫、かな",
      "startTime": 36.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 41.4392213185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、千紗ちゃんってお姉ちゃんがいるんだ～\nどんな人？　千紗ちゃんみたいな癒し系だったりして！",
      "startTime": 44.420387554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.7732213656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ……！？　私って癒し系なのかな？\nえへへ、私のお姉ちゃんは、真面目な人って感じかな",
      "startTime": 53.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね、小さい頃からずっと一緒で\n引っ込み思案な私を、よく助けてくれるの",
      "startTime": 62.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 65.8093435923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にお洋服を買いに行ったりもするし\n落ち着いてて、頼りになる、優しいお姉ちゃんだよ",
      "startTime": 68.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 73.5955338477
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ～。千紗ちゃんは、お姉ちゃんが大好き\nなんだね。気持ちが、い～っぱい伝わってきたよ！",
      "startTime": 77.1137001352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、大好きだし、尊敬もしてるんだ\nそれとね、お姉ちゃんもアイドルなの",
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 89.1730157851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　凄～い！　姉妹揃ってアイドルなんだ！\nじゃあ私も、姉妹合わせて応援するね？",
      "startTime": 93.6217657403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 97.2566823322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca007.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……でも、お仕事だからって、そんな大好きな\nお姉ちゃんと離れ離れになるなんて寂しいよね……！？",
      "startTime": 102.2550990737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 106.2458483377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca008.m4a",
      "text": "この街にいる間は、私のことをお姉ちゃんだと思って\n頼ってくれていいんだよ？",
      "startTime": 110.5217657403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 112.60151453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ありがとう。嬉しいんだけど……私、これでも\n高校二年生だし、そこまで寂しくはない……かな？",
      "startTime": 118.5999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 123.8499725022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca009.m4a",
      "text": "ラビットハウスのことも、この街のことも\nココアお姉ちゃんになんでも聞いてね！",
      "startTime": 127.1872230525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 130.0038060504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　なんだかさっきと同じ話をしてるような……？\nた、多分気のせいだよね。頼りにするね、ココアちゃん",
      "startTime": 134.866666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 140.1060513812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chn001.m4a",
      "text": "むぅ……\nココアさん、少しお話があるのですが",
      "startTime": 141.8931349749,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2020.4169270000136,
          "startTime": 142.1264683082
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 141.8931349749
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 145.6703637757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？　チノちゃんも私のこと\nお姉ちゃんって呼びたくなっちゃった？",
      "startTime": 148.7931349749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chn002.m4a",
      "text": "なんの話をしてるんですか？\n……そろそろ順番に休憩を回そうかと思います",
      "startTime": 154.5598016416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 158.3991966562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chn003.m4a",
      "text": "先ほど、雫さんとすずさんが戻られたので\nすみれさんと私で休憩してこようと思うんですが……",
      "startTime": 162.1931349749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 166.2987385429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね、時間をずらして休憩とろっか\n千紗ちゃん、休憩はチノちゃん達の次でもいい？",
      "startTime": 170.1598016416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 173.7887384094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私はまだ大丈夫だよ\nあれ？　チノちゃんはどこかにお出かけするの？",
      "startTime": 177.2333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 181.0665611581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chn004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、休憩時間中に\nすみれさんに街を案内してこようかと",
      "startTime": 183.7012912108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 186.8527486957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-cca012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～！　私も行きたい\nせっかくなら一緒に行こうよ",
      "startTime": 189.3346245442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chn005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしたら、お店が空っぽになっちゃいます",
      "startTime": 191.8007485227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 191.8007485227
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 195.8854777015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_cca_01_01-chn006.m4a",
